	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Allowing failed passwords is an interesting idea.  One that I didn't know developers even used!
<br />
<br />I think, though, I'll keep it generic.  I'm trying to develop a framework for any game.  So, if SRAM is not an option it'll default to a password screen.
<br />
<br />I'm thinking the vars could be divvied up as follows:
<br />
<br />6 8-bit (0-255) variables
<br />6 4-bit (0-15) variables
<br />5 3-bit (0-7) variables
<br />9 1-bit (true/false) variables

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


